def restore_square_vertices(x1, y1, x2, y2):
    if x1 == x2 and y1 == y2:
        return -1, -1, -1, -1

    x3 = x1 + (x2 - x1)
    y3 = y1 + (y2 - y1)
    x4 = x1 - (y2 - y1)
    y4 = y1 + (x2 - x1)
    return x3, y3, x4, y4

def main():
    x1, y1, x2, y2 = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().strip().split())
    x3, y3, x4, y4 = restore_square_vertices(x1, y1, x2, y2)
    print(x3, y3, x4, y4)
